overview: Burly Johnny Mack Brown once again plays undercover U.S. Marshal Nevada McKenzie in this overly complicated series oater from low-budget Monogram. This time, McKenzie, who goes under the alias of Roy Ferris, is waylaid by would-be stage robber Cy Manning (John Merton) en route to the Bar X Ranch.
tagline: BRAZEN BANDITS BITE THE DUST...as Johnny goes into ACTION!
title: Stranger from Santa Fe
